    <item>
      <title>由于短缺迫在眉睫，铜价飙升至历史新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-20/copper-surges-to-record-high-on-bets-of-a-looming-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，铜价攀升至历史最高水平，首次突破每吨 11,000 美元，因投资者预计供应短缺将加剧而涌入市场。马丁·里奇在彭博电视台进行报道。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-05-20/copper-surges-to-record-high-on-bets-of-a-looming-shortage</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 10:18:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Adnoc 在美国首次并购中购买 NextDecade 液化天然气项目的股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/uae-s-adnoc-to-buy-stake-in-nextdecade-s-lng-project-in-us</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉伯联合酋长国的主要石油公司购买了 NextDecade Corp. 位于德克萨斯州的天然气出口项目的股份，这是该公司在美国的首次收购，该项目也将为其提供 20 年的供应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/uae-s-adnoc-to-buy-stake-in-nextdecade-s-lng-project-in-us</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 10:09:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>WH Ireland 正在与 Zeus 洽谈出售资本市场部门</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/wh-ireland-said-in-talks-to-offload-capital-markets-unit-to-zeus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金融顾问 WH Ireland Group Plc 正在洽谈将其资本市场部门出售给英国投资银行 Zeus Capital，这是陷入困境的英国股票经纪公司中发生的最新变动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/wh-ireland-said-in-talks-to-offload-capital-markets-unit-to-zeus</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 10:00:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英国央行布罗德本特表示英国利率可能在今年夏天下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/boe-s-broadbent-says-uk-interest-rates-may-be-cut-this-summer</link>
      <description><![CDATA[副行长本·布罗德本特表示，如果第二轮通胀压力按预期消退，英国央行将能够在“夏季的某个时候”降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-20/boe-s-broadbent-says-uk-interest-rates-may-be-cut-this-summer</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 20 May 2024 09:10:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
